Sum of 3 and 5 Challenge

Create a for loop with the range from 1 to 1000 which should be "inclusive".
Condition-1: You should add all the numbers which are divisible by 3 & 5.
Print out the numbers that meet the above condition.

Condition-2: Break out of the loop once you have found 5 numbers that meet the above condition.
After breaking out of the loop,
Print the Sum of ALL the numbers that met the condition above.